parameters: Champion of Light....are you prepared to face me in battle?
You carry a soul shard...perhaps you are well equipped to
be the first one to defeat me.
You know what the shards are?
Without a Soul Shard, you cannot hurt me. No previous
champion has wielded one against me. I know from where they
came...defeat me, and not only will I lend you my strength,
but I will tell you what I know. I serve only the mighty!
